[Name] Exiv2
[Summary] Exiv2 is a C++ library and a command line utility to manage image metadata.
[Description] Exiv2 is a C++ library and a command line utility to manage image metadata. It provides fast and easy read and write access to the Exif, IPTC and XMP metadata of images in various formats. Exiv2 is available as free software and with a commercial license, and is used in many projects.
[License] GNU General Public License, Version 2
[Homepage] http://www.exiv2.org
